parameters:
\SM[rock] Ah... the hot water feels so good... \SE[28] As I
thought, hot springs are nice, aren't they...

Hehe... You've completely fallen for the hot springs,
haven't you? I'm glad I could introduce you to them.

\SE[50]If I get used to this... I won't be able to live
without it anymore...

\SE[1]How about the two of you? There wasn't a hot spring in
the village, right?

\SM[nod]Yes, I really liked it. \SE[0]I want to soak in it
every day if possible...
Um... is it not weird for me to enter the women's bath...?

It's not a problem. It's allowed to accompany until a
certain age.

\SE[0]And besides... if Ryan-kun were to be kidnapped, it
would be troublesome.
No, there's no one who would kidnap someone like me...

\SE[2]Huh? Is that so... I think Ryan is cute too, you know.
\SE[1]I'm sure there are plenty of people who would want to
kidnap him.

\SE[7]Haa...!? What are you saying? \SE[38]Laura's sense of
perception is a bit off.
That's not true, right? Right? You two also think so, right?

\SE[15]Hehe... If I were a bad person, I might have
kidnapped him.

\SE[21]Even Lunaroa-san... \SE[12]Hey Rebecca, can you say
something to her...

\SE[47]What are you saying... \SE[38]Sigh... never mind.
I'll go ahead and get out.

\SM[jump]\SE[59]No! You can't go up until you count to
100...! \SE[13]Laura! Catch him...!!

\SM[double]\SE[14]Waaah! Let go!! \!\SE[29]Stop it! Don't
rub something soft against me...!

\SE[11]Laura! Hold his arms! \!\SE[10]I'll hold down his
legs!
\SE[15]Okay! I'll show you the results of my training...!!

\SE[14]\SM[pop]Don't put all your effort into something so
trivial...! \!\SM[jump]\SE[27]Nngh...! Hey, don't touch me
in weird places...!!

\SE[11]\SM[jump]Hey, Ryan...! Don't get too excited!!
\!\SE[29]This pervert...!!

\SM[double]\SE[29]I didn't do anything...!! And besides, I
didn't do anything wrong...!!

Um, I'm sorry for intruding so often... After this, there
will be a 'reward event' prepared for clearing the quest.

...However, this game is a preliminary version. In other
words, it's difficult for me to say this, but...

No, it's not possible! I can't show you anything beyond this
point! I would be grateful if you could see it in the 'full
version'!
